BilancialTreeModel
public static final class BilancialTreeModel.ExtendedCategory
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a category, together with the additional information, whether this is a 'real' category node or the additional category node in the category itself (a boolean flag: It is true, when the object is the additional node)
